---
description: APPLY Kubernetes and Helm conventions WHEN working with helm/ directory
globs: helm/**/*.yaml
alwaysApply: false
---

- All Helm charts use apiVersion v2
- Never create Namespace, ClusterRole, or ClusterRoleBinding resources
- Never create Ingress resources — ingress and TLS are managed by infrastructure team
- Never hardcode namespace — use {{ .Release.Namespace }}
- Namespace names are provided by the infrastructure team — never auto-generate them
- Only two environments: pprod (pre-production) and prod (production) — no dev, no staging
- Values overrides: values-pprod.yaml and values-prod.yaml only (no values-dev.yaml, no values-staging.yaml)
- Service port is always 80, targetPort maps to the container port
- Exposed services use service.type: LoadBalancer, non-exposed use ClusterIP
- Use _helpers.tpl for all repeated label/name patterns
- Secrets go through Kubernetes Secrets, never ConfigMaps
- Health probes must match actual application health endpoints
- Resource requests and limits are mandatory for every container and must fit within namespace quotas
- Image registry: modelo-registry.septeo.fr/modelo/hub
- Image tags must be overridable via --set image.tag
- Only frontend and backend application services are deployed — databases, caches, and brokers are external
- Database, cache, and broker services are deployed from a separate infrastructure repository
- CI/CD pipeline builds/pushes Docker images and updates image tag in Git — deployment is handled by ArgoCD (GitOps)
- Pipeline uses BB_TOKEN for GitOps commit with [skip ci] to avoid loops
- Database migrations run as ArgoCD PreSync Jobs (one-shot, fail-closed) — never in application pods
- Entrypoints check `SKIP_MIGRATIONS=true` (set in ConfigMap) to skip migrations in K8s pods
- Seed Jobs are optional, gated by `seed.enabled` in values.yaml (default false in production)
- Migration Jobs use `argocd.argoproj.io/hook: PreSync` and `hook-delete-policy: BeforeHookCreation`
- Seed Jobs use `argocd.argoproj.io/sync-wave: "1"` to run after migration Jobs complete
